By Air
Mahanbari Airport, Dibrugarh is the nearest airport to World War II Cemetery, near Jairampur and distance from airport is about 141 kilometers
By Railway
Ledo Railway Station is the nearest local passenger railway station to World War II Cemetery near Jairampur and distance from Ledo railway station is 40 kilometers. Tinsukia Railway station is the nearest long distance Express Railway station to World War II Cemetery near Jairampur and distance from station is about 100 kilometers
By Road
Jairampur is the nearest bus station to World War II Cemetery and distance from bus station is 6 kilometers. From Assam, Tisukia and Margherita, one can hire taxi or avail government transport services for visiting World War II Cemetery near Jairampur.
