ACCESSIBILITY
The department shall aim to make tourist destinations,
accommodation units, and wayside amenities greatly accessible
to people with disabilities. At major tourist destinations, there
shall be provision of ramps wherever feasible, and shall have toilet
facilities amenable to persons with disabilities. Accommodation
units like hotels and resorts rated 2-stars and above shall be
mandated to have one washroom on each ␀oor for persons
with disabilities.
