The policy aims to present Arunachal Pradesh as a warm,
welcoming, safe, and a tourist-friendly destination. The success
of any tourist destination hinges on its ability to make visitors
feel comfortable in navigating and interacting with the people
without worrying about issues such as hustling, cheating, or
harassment by the local touts.
